Payfort :
*it is payment gateway . it is used to accept online payments via credit card through FORT,  .We can integrate this payment gateway in our project with secure payment for customers .

*based on PCI (Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard) ,Payfort chose amazon as cloud provider and run FORT entirely on AWS technologies. 
* Sensitive financial data is stored in Amazon Simple Storage Service .
*PayFort operates in the US East (N. Virginia) and US West (Oregon) AWS Regions.
*PayFort runs its Oracle database on Amazon Relational Database Service (Amazon RDS),
and using CloudHSM encryption service(cloud-based hardware security module (HSM) ) that enale us to generate and use our own encryption keys on the AWS Cloud.

